      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car and it\u2019s looking for a brand new home. It\u2019s been really well-maintained and is in great shape, perfect for someone who wants a reliable, smooth ride without any of the stress. It\u2019s super clean inside and out, and honestly, it\u2019s just a joy to drive. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how well it\u2019s been cared for!",
