    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the perfect example of a well-loved daily driver that has been maintained with an open checkbook. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with city parking. Inside, the cabin remains a premium environment; the leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one, and the smoke-free interior still smells fresh. All electronic components, including the heated seats, navigation system, and sunroof, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in its prime. It has a documented service history, with a recent oil change and a brake fluid flush performed last month. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the transmission shifts smoothly through every gear. While not a showroom trailer-queen, this car is reliable, aesthetically pleasing, and ready for its next owner to drive home with total confidence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
