      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s in wonderful shape and has plenty of life left in it! It\u2019s been super reliable for me, and I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with everything it needs. If you\u2019re looking for a smooth ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
